service.Event Name: Blow balloons and assemble the balloon arc
service.Details: OLs & OIs to meet in school at 0600 to blow balloons and assemble the balloon arc, to be up by 0645.

By 0645: OLs to line up at the Main Gate to welcome Sec 1s. Other OLs to be stationed at the parade square with the signs of the Sec 1 classes.

One OL will hold the signs for each class, while another escorts the Sec 1s to them and line them up.

service.Event Name: School Leader Talks + Recess + CM Time
service.Details:
OLs to go back to class and leave with their bags at 1030 to start preparing for Orientation.

OLs to bring their PLDs to present the Google Slides.

service.Event Name: Camp Introduction & OLs Introduction & OIs Introduction
service.Details: OLs to introduce Camp Coronation and themselves, using the Google Slides at hand as well. OIs to go around and introduce themselves.
OLs to play icebreaker games. Snackbreak at any time the OLs want.
OLs to play energiser games.
Arrange the chairs back.

OLs to debrief the class based on their observation. OLs to brief the class on what to expect the next day.

Remind the Sec 1s to tell them their packing list. OLs to remind Sec 1s to bring coloured paper, stapler, etc. to decorate class notice boards and their ties.

service.Details:
Recess for classes having recess
OLs together with the sec 1 class to brainstorm class cheer, flag, and noticeboard ideas.
OLs, to collect the flag materials from the OIs
OLs to split the class up/choose what to tackle first.
OIs will pass OLs the flag

service.Event Name: Learning to tie a tie +  School song + School creed
service.Details:
Learning to tie a tie [15-20min]
OLs refer to the slides/video to teach the sec 1s how to tie a tie.
ALL OLs MUST know how to tie a tie.

School Song [45 mins]
OLs to show the slides on the school song and ensure students roughly remember the school song.
OLs to guide them on how the school song tune goes so that they have a rough idea on the tune.
*OLs can play a game to test whether they remember the school song just by playing the music and asking them to sing.

School Creed[20-25 mins]
OLs, show the slides to the Sec 1s and guide them to memorise the school creed.

OIs to deliver the provided food and trashbags to the Classrooms.

OLs to make trash bins using chairs in the classroom for the Sec 1s to separate from lunchboxes, cutlery, drink packets and food wastage.
OLs to follow along their Classes to the different CCA Experiences.
